                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The sludge troll takes cold or fire damage</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The sludge troll makes a sludge cough Strike against a random creature within their first range increment. If the troll is taking persistent fire damage, they attempt a @Check[flat|dc:15] to remove it.</p>"
