                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The sludge troll is hiding in water, and a creature that hasn't detected it is within 30 feet</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The sludge troll Swims, then Leaps at the end of its Swim action, landing on any solid surface adjacent to the water. Once the triggering creature is in the troll's first range increment, the sludge troll makes a sludge cough Strike against the creature with a +2 circumstance bonus to the attack roll.</p>"
